OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCalls for Post Office      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpolice probe after BBC     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstory                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former sub-postmasters and politicians 
OL,6, have called for the Post Office to face
OL,7, a police investigation after BBC News  
OL,8, revealed the company knew of flaws in  
OL,9, its Horizon IT system.                 
OL,11,FA document shows bosses and lawyers    
OL,12,Fknew of issues in 2017, but kept       
OL,13,Farguing sub-postmasters were to blame. 
OL,15,FMP Kevan Jones said "the police need to
OL,16,Fstart looking at this" specific point  
OL,17,Fraised in the BBC investigation.       
OL,19,FThe Post Office earlier said it would  
OL,20,Fbe "inappropriate to comment".         
